{"tid":2221870,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】科大南沙分校正式動工 2022年開校","createTime":"2020-09-28T16:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T18:22:59.000Z","uid":225931,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19e5d1806e56c3c1a798a86de8e280ba4ea2e9ad","tid":2221870,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"新校園首階段將先招收研究生，待條件許可後也會招收本科生。校園建築風格將與科大一脈相承，建築規劃以配合四大樞紐定位相關的教學和研究活動為主軸，輔以生活配套和住宿設施，並以通達無障礙的室內學術走廊連接各學術單位。新校園還將參照國際標準及傳承科大可持續智慧校園理念，利用自然地景、特別是毗鄰的水道優勢，依水而建，與建築共融，致力創建綠色智慧校園。新校園亦將在大學廣場，放置一個與清水灣校園一樣的日晷雕塑。第一期建設工程預計於2022年中完成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ust.hk/sites/default/files/2019-09/perspective-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ust.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2019-09%2Fperspective-1.jpg&h=7d805a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ust.hk/sites/default/files/2019-09/perspective-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ust.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2019-09%2Fperspective-2.jpg&h=f30f5dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ust.hk/sites/default/files/2019-09/Program_English_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ust.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2019-09%2FProgram_English_1.jpg&h=e9b9d6f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ec531227bc9f7637bc56c60043d54f65a5853ee","tid":2221870,"uid":53922,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"幾時整個香港政府深圳分部？"},{"pid":"97b6191270797a41eaa67d8365d52dabed31abc0","tid":2221870,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d1embwjxo27ph2.cloudfront.net/actions/nmcImages/image/generateImage?v=5&amp;anchor=top&amp;height=675&amp;width=1200&amp;path=%2FHKUST-GZ-c-KPF-5-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd1embwjxo27ph2.cloudfront.net%2Factions%2FnmcImages%2Fimage%2FgenerateImage%3Fv%